"title": "5568: suffering, causes of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5568: suffering, causes of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The ultimate cause of suffering is sin, which has brought violence, disease and death into the world. All suffering, however, is under the sovereign purpose of God, who is able to use it for his glory.</p>\n<h2>The ultimate cause of suffering is sin</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:14-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:14–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:1\">JOB 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:1-John9:3\">JHN 9:1–9:3</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:6-Job5:7\">JOB 5:6–5:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12-Rom5:14\">ROM 5:12–5:14</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering as a result of human wickedness</h2>\n<h3>Murder</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:8\">GEN 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:5-Gen49:7\">GEN 49:5–49:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:10-1Sam18:11\">1SA 18:10–18:11</a></p>\n<h3>Injury</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:67\">MAT 26:67</a></p>\n<h3>Cruelty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:4\">PSA 71:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg1:7\">JDG 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps54:3\">PSA 54:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:13\">AMO 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:16-Matt2:18\">MAT 2:16–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:30\">LUK 10:30</a></p>\n<h3>Rioting</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:17\">2KI 7:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:22\">ACT 16:22</a></p>\n<h3>Warfare</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:22\">JER 50:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:1-Gen14:2\">GEN 14:1–14:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:11-Gen14:12\">GEN 14:11–14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:17\">EXO 13:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:20-Josh6:21\">JOS 6:20–6:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:22-Josh10:26\">JOS 10:22–10:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg1:4-Judg1:7\">JDG 1:4–1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:35\">1KI 22:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:5-2Kgs17:6\">2KI 17:5–17:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:2\">ZEC 14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:20-Luke21:24\">LUK 21:20–21:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:4\">REV 6:4</a></p>\n<h3>Injustice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:9\">EZK 9:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:19-Gen39:20\">GEN 39:19–39:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:11-1Kgs21:14\">1KI 21:11–21:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:16\">2KI 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:1-Ps58:2\">PSA 58:1–58:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:6\">PSA 64:6</a></p>\n<h3>Oppression</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:1\">ECC 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:11\">EXO 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:1-1Kgs12:4\">1KI 12:1–12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:12-1Kgs12:14\">1KI 12:12–12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:5\">PSA 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1-Jas5:6\">JAS 5:1–5:6</a></p>\n<h3>Adultery</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:9\">2SA 12:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:14\">MAL 2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Theft</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:19\">GEN 31:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:14-Job1:15\">JOB 1:14–1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:17\">JOB 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:2\">JOB 24:2</a></p>\n<h3>Broken relationships</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:14-Job19:19\">JOB 19:14–19:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:10\">PSA 27:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:28\">PRO 16:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:39\">ACT 15:39</a></p>\n<h3>Hatred</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:3\">PSA 109:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:15\">2SA 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:3\">TIT 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Jealousy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:4\">GEN 37:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:4-Gen4:5\">GEN 4:4–4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:6\">GEN 16:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:8-Gen21:10\">GEN 21:8–21:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:8-1Sam18:9\">1SA 18:8–18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:18\">MAT 27:18</a></p>\n<h3>Persecution</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:20\">JHN 15:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6\">JER 38:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:4-Dan3:6\">DAN 3:4–3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:7\">DAN 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:10-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:10–5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:35-Matt10:36\">MAT 10:35–10:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:9-Rev6:11\">REV 6:9–6:11</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering as a result of misfortune</h2>\n<h3>Accidents</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:4\">2SA 4:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:2\">2KI 1:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:4\">LUK 13:4</a></p>\n<h3>Sickness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:1\">GEN 48:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:1\">2KI 20:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:7\">JOB 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:10\">PSA 42:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:6\">MAT 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:8\">ACT 28:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:27\">PHP 2:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:20\">2TI 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:14\">JAS 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Hunger and want</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10\">GEN 12:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:3\">JOB 30:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:13\">ISA 5:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:42-Matt25:43\">MAT 25:42–25:43</a></p>\n<h3>Natural disasters</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:48\">1KI 22:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:16\">JOB 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:18-Job1:19\">JOB 1:18–1:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:6\">ISA 29:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:4\">JOL 1:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:5\">ZEC 14:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:7\">MAT 24:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:18-Acts27:20\">ACT 27:18–27:20</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering through old age and death</h2>\n<h3>Ageing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:34-2Sam19:35\">2SA 19:34–19:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:9\">PSA 71:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:1\">ECC 12:1</a></p>\n<h3>Bereavement</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:1-Gen23:2\">GEN 23:1–23:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:18-Job1:19\">JOB 1:18–1:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:11-Luke7:13\">LUK 7:11–7:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:33-John11:35\">JHN 11:33–11:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering through anxiety</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:25\">PRO 12:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:65-Deut28:67\">DEU 28:65–28:67</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:26\">LUK 21:26</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering through foolishness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:17\">PSA 107:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:34-Judg11:36\">JDG 11:34–11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:1\">PRO 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:15\">PRO 11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:1\">PRO 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:29-Prov23:30\">PRO 23:29–23:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:17\">LUK 15:17</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering through Satanic activity</h2>\n<h3>The influence of Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1\">GEN 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:12\">JOB 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:6-Job2:7\">JOB 2:6–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:16\">LUK 13:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:19\">1JN 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:7-Rev20:8\">REV 20:7–20:8</a></p>\n<h3>Demon-possession</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:28\">MAT 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:22\">MAT 12:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:22\">MAT 15:22</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering brought about by God himself</h2>\n<h3>All suffering comes within his will</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:3\">JHN 9:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11\">EPH 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Some suffering is for his immediate glory</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:19\">JHN 21:19</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's suffering produces salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:10\">ISA 53:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a></p>\n<h3>Christian suffering produces good fruits</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:4\">ROM 5:3–5:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:9\">2CO 1:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:11\">HEB 12:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2\">JAS 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:3\">JAS 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>God's people must be disciplined</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:7\">HEB 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:35\">EXO 32:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:13-2Sam12:14\">2SA 12:13–12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:67\">PSA 119:67</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:71\">PSA 119:71</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:11-Prov3:12\">PRO 3:11–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:8-Heb12:11\">HEB 12:8–12:11</a></p>\n<h3>The wicked must be punished</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5-Gen6:7\">GEN 6:5–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:14\">JHN 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8\">2TH 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:4\">REV 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:15\">REV 20:15</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering accepted voluntarily</h2>\n<h3>By Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3-Isa53:5\">ISA 53:3–53:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:10\">ISA 53:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a></p>\n<h3>By his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:15\">2CO 12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:10-2Cor4:12\">2CO 4:10–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:35\">HEB 11:35</a></p>\n<h3>For the good of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:13\">JHN 15:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:7\">ROM 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:18\">PHM 1:18</a></p>",
